Screenz Android App

Overview
    Android utility app for quickly finding out some key information about the device's display and its capabilities. 
    
    Useful during development aimed at supporting UIs across multiple screen sizes and densities. 
    
    Particularly well suited for use in automated test environments.

Release Notes:
    Version 0.0.2: 
        * Now also displays screen size in dp units
		* Display cleaned up a bit
		* Code cleaned a bit as well

    Version 0.0.1:
        * First release published to Android Market.